https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/x1CTGQrbmKqLhm7xcXoXlPKSUnd.jpg Emily has just been dumped by her girlfriend, kicked out of her apartment, and fired from her job. Her best friend hooks her up with a new gig: personal assistant to a dominatrix. But when Emily falls for her new boss -- and her new boss's boyfriend -- she must decide what risks are worth taking for love. 2 in the Bush is an unconventional romantic comedy about dungeons, a fish named Archimedes, and the many forms that love takes. 2 In the Bush: A Love Story
